Planets3D is a 3D gravitational simulator inspired by Planets (planets.homedns.org)

Build using CMake (www.cmake.org)

Dependencies:
Qt 4.8 or 5 (qt-project.org) (Qt 5 must be 5.1 or later or desktop OpenGL build, to use Qt 4.8 enable option PLANETS3D_USE_QT4)
GLM (glm.g-truc.net/)
TinyXml (www.grinninglizard.com/tinyxml/)
